Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:47.56,town_OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,ねぇ　好きなの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.64,0:00:49.28,town_OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,気付いてた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.38,0:00:52.61,town_OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,多分　君に恋してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.73,0:00:54.10,town_OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,ちっぽけで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.26,0:00:59.04,town_OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,弱虫なセンチメンタルラブ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.95,0:01:11.23,town_OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,会いたいって思う瞬間が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.47,0:01:18.13,town_OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,いつからか溢れるようになって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.86,0:01:23.22,town_OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,傷つくのが怖くて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.32,0:01:28.32,town_OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,わざと冷たくしてしまうんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.09,0:01:33.46,town_OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,でも本当は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.48,0:01:37.81,town_OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,臆病なあたしに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.04,0:01:44.03,town_OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,今すぐ気付いてほしいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.91,0:01:46.58,town_OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,ねぇ　好きなの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:48.35,town_OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,気付いてた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.55,0:01:51.78,town_OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,多分　君に恋してる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:55.08,town_OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,気持ち　伝えたいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.44,0:01:58.98,town_OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,センチメンタル　邪魔してる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.12,0:02:00.47,town_OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,ねぇ　キスして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.65,0:02:02.18,town_OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.44,0:02:05.56,town_OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,なんて言えたなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.59,0:02:08.94,town_OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,あたしの　知らない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:13.90,town_OP_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,君に会えるのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,town_jp,NTP,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.42,0:19:04.64,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,君の手紙を読んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.48,0:19:08.84,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,終わったはずの午後に
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:11.92,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,それが全部嘘だと
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:16.04,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,僕にはわかったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.56,0:19:19.45,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,悲しいときでさえも
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.47,0:19:23.15,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,笑ってしまう君を
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:26.82,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,守ると言った言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:29.96,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘にはしたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:33.73,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,アイツらだって
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.55,0:19:37.84,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,わかってくれるはず
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:42.81,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,僕も行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:47.08,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,君のいる町
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:51.66,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,どんな答えが待っていても
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.91,0:19:55.04,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,構わないから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:58.86,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,そこへ行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.39,0:20:02.01,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,君のいる町
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.73,0:20:04.92,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,君の心が
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.06,0:20:09.46,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,僕を呼んでいるのが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:14.02,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,僕も行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.14,0:20:17.00,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,君のいる町
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:19.68,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,君の心が
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:24.32,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,僕を呼んでいるのが
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:28.28,town_ED_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,聞こえるから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.88,0:20:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,
